        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hey {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>It seems that every newsletter in my in-box this week is filled with economic doom and gloom, but as there's little or nothing most of us can do about that, I'm trying to focus on things I can control ‚Äî like my desk, which is the tidiest it's been for years. For once, it's not just about procrastination, it's about trying to get our house into a position we only have to heat the minimum number of rooms‚Ä¶</p><p>There's a lot on my mind this week, with teaching starting at City, and my newsletter course well underway. In particular, I'm back working on the long-promised piece on newsletter analytics. not least because the platform I use, <a href=\"https://ghost.org\">Ghost</a>, has just upgraded its own metrics. Watch for more on that later in the week.</p><p>In the meantime, here's a few interesting things that have crossed my desk in the last few days.</p>"
